{"about_the_game":"This is the free Chapter 0 to <strong>Time Survivors</strong>, a rogue-like bullet hell game where you can <strong>play as legendary historical characters</strong> like Abe Lincoln, Tesla, Cleopatra, and more, each now wielding unique custom abilities that revolutionize gameplay. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/title_Unique_Abilities.png?t=1728317352\" /><br>Transform into a flying ninja robot as Oda Nobunaga, create defensive barriers made of cherry trees as Abe Lincoln, or set the battlefield ablaze as Nero - the choice is yours. Each character brings<strong> a unique touch to every run</strong>, making each playthrough a unique adventure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/Nik-fight-with-electrode,-no-hud,-framed-616x250.gif?t=1728317352\" /><br>Travel through time and <strong>fight hordes</strong> of memorable enemies as you unravel a mystery. With over 150 different weapons, items, Relics, and buffs to choose from, every run is a unique experience. Fight skeletons in the Medieval Age, Velociraptors and T-Rexes in the Stone Age, and discover plenty of quests and secrets along the way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/title_Meta-progression_map.png?t=1728317352\" /><br>But that's not all - Time Survivors: Chapter 0 presents a new meta progression system, allowing you to unlock and upgrade characters, weapons, and stages, even <strong>game mode modifiers</strong>, using gold and resources collected during your runs. Tailor your progression to your preferred playstyle and strategically <strong>allocate resources</strong> to create your own game-breaking build.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/Meta_map_tree_-_620x360.gif?t=1728317352\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/title_whats_in_chapter_0.png?t=1728317352\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 stages full of enemies, secrets, mini bosses  and end-stage bosses: The Dark Age and The Stone Age<br></li><li>8 unlockable characters from the entire human history, <strong>each with their own unique ability</strong>!<br></li><li>32 different weapons and buffs to choose from for a unique experience every run<br></li><li>8 Cursed Relics<br></li><li>41 different enemies<br></li><li>35 Unlockables</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/title_what_you_always_get.png?t=1728317352\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as epic historic characters, each with their unique ability<br></li><li>Tree-based meta progression for all elements in the game<br></li><li>Casual quick 20 minute play sessions + plenty of quests and secrets to discover<br></li><li>A Sandbox mode to test any overpowered build and train against any enemy</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/extras/721---Nero-ability_OPTIMIZED.gif?t=1728317352\" /><br><br><br>And since you've come this far... don't forget to <strong>wishlist the full game</strong> to stay up-to-date on the latest features and updates!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728317352","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/page.bg.jpg?t=1728317352","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728317352","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455500/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728317352","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","